data.description: Rare opportunity to own this beautiful home in the highly sought-after Legacy Reserve village of Smith Farm; a prestigious gated community with private resort style amenities.This spacious home boasts an open floor plan w/plenty of room for entertaining. Gourmet kitchen comes complete w/ island, breakfast nook & pantry. Large, separate downstairs bedroom can be used as a nanny suite or private office. Upstairs Master w/ walk in closet & balcony has 5th bedroom combined as a master suite which can be used as an office, nursery, or converted back to a bedroom. Master bath includes a large tub, separate shower & his/her vanities. Home is in a great school district, walking distance from the elementary school. All measurements and sizes are approximate. Buyers responsibility to verify
